@startuml folio-sequence-submit-peer-review
' Folio — Reviewer submits review (UC-04)
' Render: https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml

title Submit peer review (UC-04)

actor Reviewer
participant "Folio UI" as UI
participant "Backend API\n(NestJS)" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "Email service" as Email

Reviewer -> UI : Read manuscript;\nenter comments & recommendation
Reviewer -> UI : Tap **Submit review**
UI -> API : POST .../assignments/:slug/review

alt Not accepted / empty comments / already submitted
  API --> UI : 400 error
  UI --> Reviewer : Show message
else Success
  API -> DB : BEGIN transaction
  API -> DB : INSERT review
  API -> DB : UPDATE assignment\nstatus = **completed**
  API -> DB : In-app notifications +\noutbox (review.submitted)
  API -> DB : COMMIT

  API -> MQ : Publish events
  API --> UI : Review saved
  UI --> Reviewer : Confirmation

  MQ -> Email : Notify editors /\njournal managers
end

@enduml
